## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of data up to October 2023 and may not capture the most recent developments in mental health support and attitudes. Additionally, while the report draws on a range of sources, it may not fully represent the diversity of experiences and perspectives across different cultures and regions. Further research is needed to explore these aspects comprehensively.

